---
title: Chicken Caprese Pasta Salad served warm with Basil and Lemon
description: While we’ll take the classic combo of mozzarella, tomato, and basil in pretty much any form, when our chefs let us know they transformed caprese into a hearty pasta dinner, we could barely contain ourselves. Here, orecchiette (that’s Italian for “little ears!”) is tossed with Italian-spiced chicken, juicy tomatoes, and creamy mozzarella in a lemony basil vinaigrette. Need we say more?
